column5: hey guys just got back from a week vacation with my gf in jamaica....The pics will be on my comp later this week ....I did manage to go fishing however ,caught a few small fish and had a chance at some tarpon.. Anyway i just got back early this morn and im itching to go fishing ....I called all my fishing buds but its a no go from them ..If anyone wants to hook up fpr an afternoon of fishing on simcoe for some pike let me know......I have my boat and all my gear . Ill be leaving my house at the latest 2;30 , so if i dont find anyone by then im going solo
Argh! Such a tempting proposition pike..... Wish I could get away from work... Catch one for me.
